'''''Silver Chariot, Part With That Humanity's Epic''''' is a [[Trailblaze Mission]] in the chapter [[As Tomorrow Became Yesterday]].

==Steps==
# Return to the Express and search for your companions' whereabouts
# Cyrene's choice after the fall of Irontomb
# Why is the Express completely empty? I need to get to the bottom of this...
# Investigate the strange noise from the bathroom
# Find Castorice hiding in the bathtub
# Big farewell to this epic journey through Amphoreus
# Cyrene's choice after the fall of Irontomb
# Head to the Party Car and say hi to your fellow Chrysos Heir companions
# Talk to the Chrysos Heirs present
# Go to the Parlor Car and find Phainon
# Talk to Hysilens and Anaxa
# Chat with Phainon

